content: 余京津 Yu Jingjin | Life, Space-Time, and Beyond Bits & Pieces 2024-07-11 During the heat of the COVID-19 pandemic days, I learned flutter/dart and wrote a game (app) related to some of my research interests in multi-robot path planning. The video below explains what the game, pebbles, does You can get it on Andriod and iOS.
